OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVariable amounts of cloud but a
OL,6,Fgenerally fine, bright and rather warm
OL,7,Fday. Cloud increasing during the
OL,8,Fafternoon, perhaps bringing some rain,
OL,9,Fmainly across western hills by early
OL,10,Fevening. Breezy at times, with
OL,11,Foccasional gusty winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FTurning cloudy across all
OL,14,Fparts through the evening with
OL,15,Foutbreaks of mainly light rain
OL,16,Fspreading east overnight. More
OL,17,Fpersistent rain with heavier bursts
OL,18,Flikely in the far west around dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
